
#### Code snippet to add inside `NanoVelcroCouplingSystem` (audited emergency_release)
```python
    def emergency_release(self):
        """
        Hardware/watchdog style emergency release that forces disengage without interactive auth.
        This is intended for hardware watchdogs or automated safety systems only.
        All uses are logged in support_logs for audit.
        """
        if not self.engaged:
            logger.info("No emergency release needed; system not engaged.")
            return False
        logger.warning("AUTO EMERGENCY RELEASE invoked by watchdog. Forcing safe disengage.")
        self.support_logs.append("AUTO EMERGENCY RELEASE ACTIVATED")
        # Force safe disengage but keep audit trail
        self._safe_disengage()
        return True
